install go module as 
* go mod init

then install releted packages using in project 

protoc --> go get google.golang.org/protobuf/cmd/protoc-gen-go
grpc --> go get google.golang.org/grpc
protobuf ---> go get github.com/golang/protobuf


List current module and all dependencies 
* go list -m all

once done need to change from inderect to direct need to do in go.mod
* go mod vendor



